Florida Ice Manufacturing Co., a Corporation, Appellant, v. The Rust Boiler Company, a Corporation, Appellee. (Supreme Court of Florida, En Banc, June Term, 1909.) Fletcher & Dodge, for Appellant. Cooper & Cooper, for Appellee. Circuit Court of Duval County; E. M. Call, Judge.

Decree in favor of appellee. Appeal dismissed on motion of counsel for appellant.
